skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pie time
des:
This skill is a recipe skills, for the upcoming holidays. Whether you're a baker or a novice, this skill will help you impress your friends and family. there's even a quiz to show what the pies should look like. 

(For Spot users. the pictures show in numerical order. so the first picture is one, the second is two and so on. tap to the left or right to swipe through the pictures) 

((For Echo or Dot users, Ask the skill to read the information to you once you have selected your pie))
